AI and hospital pricing

You’re right that healthcare pricing is often opaque and inconsistent. AI could help in several practical ways:

1. Price transparency tools
	•	Aggregating hospital billing data and insurance contracts
	•	Predicting expected costs before a procedure

2. Fraud and billing error detection
	•	Flagging unusual billing patterns
	•	Catching duplicate or incorrect codes

3. Resource optimization
	•	Predicting patient demand
	•	Improving scheduling and staffing

4. Negotiation analysis
	•	Helping hospitals and insurers compare costs and outcomes across regions

Many of these ideas are already being tested because healthcare billing systems generate huge datasets that are difficult for humans to analyze manually.

